## Why This Is Asked
Assesses practical ability to automate cross-region SAP DR testing using cloud-native tools, with measurable RPO/RTO and auditable results.

## Key Concepts
- SAP HANA MDC cross-region replication
- AWS Fault Injection Simulator (FIS)
- AWS Step Functions orchestration
- Validation, rollback, and auditability across regions

## Code Example
```javascript
// Minimal example of starting a Step Functions execution
import { SFClient, StartExecutionCommand } from "@aws-sdk/client-sfn";

const client = new SFClient({ region: "us-west-2" });
async function start() {
  const cmd = new StartExecutionCommand({ stateMachineArn: "arn:aws:states:us-west-2:123456789012:stateMachine:DRTest" });
  const res = await client.send(cmd);
  console.log(res.executionArn);
}
start();
```

