## Why This Is Asked
This question tests practical use of AWS-native tooling to monitor SAP workloads, focusing on a low-friction, maintainable health check at a beginner level, with clear failure criteria and automated reporting.

## Key Concepts
- Event-driven health checks with EventBridge and Lambda
- AWS Systems Manager Run Command for remote execution
- SAP health probes (sapcontrol, HANA via SQL)
- S3 JSON output, SNS alerts, IAM least-privilege
